  "english": [
    "<strong>MISHNA:</strong> <b>One may bring wood</b> chopped from a tree the previous day <b>from</b> an unfenced <b>field,</b> but only <b>from that which has been gathered</b> into a pile before the Festival for the purpose of using it for kindling. However, scattered wood is <i>muktze</i> and may not be handled. <b>And</b> if one brings wood <b>from a <i>karpef</i></b> used for storage, he may bring <b>even from the scattered</b> wood, as it is considered a guarded courtyard rather than a field, and one does not remove even scattered items from his mind if they are stored inside such an enclosure. The mishna explains: <b>What is a <i>karpef</i>?</b> It is <b>any</b> enclosure <b>that is near a city,</b> but if it is far from a city, it is considered a field; this is <b>the statement of Rabbi Yehuda. Rabbi Yosei says: Any</b> fenced place <b>into which one</b> can <b>enter</b> only <b>with a key</b> is a <i>karpef</i>, <b>even</b> if it is located at a distance from a city, provided that it is <b>within the Shabbat limit.</b>",
    "<strong>GEMARA:</strong> <b>Rav Yehuda said</b> that <b>Shmuel said: One may not bring wood except from</b> the wood that was <b>gathered in a <i>karpef</i>.</b> The Gemara challenges: <b>But didn’t we learn</b> in the mishna: And <b>from a <i>karpef</i>, even from scattered</b> wood? The Gemara answers: <b>The mishna</b> follows <b>an individual</b> opinion.",
    "One may not rely on it, as is clear from a different source that the majority view is otherwise, <b>as it is taught</b> in a <i>baraita</i> that <b>Rabbi Shimon ben Elazar said: Beit Shammai and Beit Hillel did not disagree with regard to</b> wood <b>scattered in fields that one may not bring</b> it on a Festival to one’s house for kindling, <b>nor with regard to</b> wood <b>gathered in a <i>karpef</i> that one may bring</b> it. <b>With regard to what did they disagree?</b> It is <b>with regard to scattered</b> wood <b>in a <i>karpef</i> and gathered</b> wood <b>in fields, as Beit Shammai say: He may not bring</b> it, <b>and Beit Hillel say: He may bring</b> it. Although the lenient opinion with regard to gathered wood in a field is attributed to Beit Hillel, this is only according to the minority view of Rabbi Shimon ben Elazar. However, most Sages disagree and say that one may not bring wood from a field at all, even according to Beit Hillel.",
    "<b>Rava said:</b> With regard to <b>reed leaves and vine leaves, although they are gathered</b> together <b>and placed</b> in the same spot, <b>since if a wind comes it will scatter them,</b> they <b>are</b> already <b>considered scattered and are</b> therefore <b>prohibited.</b> Given that they are likely to be scattered in the wind, one does not intend to use them. However, <b>if one placed a vessel on them the day before</b> to prevent their being scattered in the wind, <b>it seems well</b> and is permitted.",
    "The mishna discussed the question: <b>What is a <i>karpef</i>?</b> Rabbi Yehuda states that it is any enclosure that is near a city, while in Rabbi Yosei’s opinion it is any fenced place into which one can enter only with a key, provided that it is within the Shabbat limit of a city. <b>A dilemma was raised before</b> the Sages: With regard to <b>what</b> case <b>is</b> the mishna <b>speaking?</b> Does Rabbi Yehuda mean to say that a <i>karpef</i> is <b>any</b> place <b>that is near a city, provided that it has a key,</b> otherwise it is not a <i>karpef</i> at all; <b>and Rabbi Yosei comes to say: Since it has a key, even</b> if it is not near a city, as long as it is <b>within the Shabbat limit</b> it is <b>also</b> considered a <i>karpef</i>? According to this understanding, Rabbi Yosei’s view is more lenient than that of Rabbi Yehuda.",
    "<b>Or perhaps this is what</b> Rabbi Yehuda <b>is saying: Any</b> enclosure <b>that is near a city</b> is a <i>karpef</i>, <b>whether it has a key or does not have a key, and Rabbi Yosei comes to say:</b> With regard to the distance, it is a <i>karpef</i> <b>even</b> if it is not near a city, provided that it is <b>within the Shabbat limit, but specifically if it has a key. However, if it does not have a key, even</b> if it is <b>near a city</b> it is <b>also not</b> considered a <i>karpef</i>. According to this understanding, the opinion of Rabbi Yosei is not necessarily the more lenient one; rather, for him the defining issue is whether or not there is a key, regardless of distance.",
    "The Gemara answers: <b>Come</b> and <b>hear from</b> the fact <b>that it is taught</b> in the mishna that <b>Rabbi Yosei says: Any</b> place <b>into which one enters with a key, even within the Shabbat limit,</b> and he does not say: If one enters, but rather: Any place into which one enters, it shows that the key is not the determining factor. One may <b>learn from this</b> that <b>Rabbi Yosei stated two</b> conditions <b>as leniencies.</b> In other words, he is not more stringent than Rabbi Yehuda in any situation; he is lenient in all cases. The Gemara concludes: Indeed, <b>learn from here</b> that this is the case. <b>Rav Salla said</b> that <b>Rabbi Yirmeya said:</b> The <b><i>halakha</i></b> is <b>in accordance with</b> the opinion of <b>Rabbi Yosei as a leniency;</b> Rabbi Yosei should be understood in this manner, and one should rule accordingly.",
    "<strong>MISHNA:</strong> <b>One may not chop wood</b> on a Festival <b>neither from beams</b> intended for construction <b>nor from a beam that broke on a Festival,</b> although it no longer serves any purpose. <b>And one may not chop</b> wood on a Festival, <b>neither with an ax, nor with a saw, nor with a sickle,</b> as these are clearly craftsman’s tools used on weekdays. <b>Rather, one may</b> chop only <b>with a cleaver.</b> Using this tool differs greatly from the weekday manner in which wood is chopped."
  ],
  "gemara": [
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"151\" data-sentence-id=\"0\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"א\"></span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>מַתְנִי׳</strong></big> מְבִיאִין עֵצִים מִן הַשָּׂדֶה — מִן הַמְכוּנָּס,",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וּמִן הַקַּרְפֵּף — אֲפִילּוּ מִן הַמְפוּזָּר. אֵיזֶהוּ קַרְפֵּף — כׇּל",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שֶׁסָּמוּךְ לְעִיר, דִּבְרֵי <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda bar Rabbi Elai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1395\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda bar Rabbi Elai\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה ברבי אילעאי\">רַבִּי יְהוּדָה</span>. <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yosei, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1657\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yosei\" data-name-he=\"רבי יוסי בן חלפתא\">רַבִּי יוֹסֵי</span> אוֹמֵר:",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כׇּל שֶׁנִּכְנָסִין לוֹ בְּפוֹתַחַת, וַאֲפִילּוּ בְּתוֹךְ תְּחוּם",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שַׁבָּת<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"164\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"152\" data-sentence-id=\"1\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"ב\"></span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>גְּמָ׳</strong></big> אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Yehuda bar Yeḥezkel, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1394\" data-full-name=\"Rav Yehuda bar Yeḥezkel\" data-name-he=\"רב יהודה בר יחזקאל\">רַב יְהוּדָה</span> אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Shmuel II, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2763\" data-full-name=\"Shmuel II\" data-name-he=\"שמואל\">שְׁמוּאֵל</span>:",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֵין מְבִיאִין עֵצִים אֶלָּא מִן הַמְכוּנָּסִין שֶׁבַּקַּרְפֵּף.",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְהָא אֲנַן תְּנַן: מִן הַקַּרְפֵּף — וַאֲפִילּוּ מִן הַמְפוּזָּרִים!",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מַתְנִיתִין יְחִידָאָה הִיא. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>דְּתַנְיָא, אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yishmael ben Elazar, sixth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2846\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yishmael ben Elazar\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן אלעזר\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-16736\">רַבִּי שִׁמְעוֹן בֶּן</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yishmael ben Elazar, sixth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2846\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yishmael ben Elazar\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן אלעזר\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-16736\">אֶלְעָזָר</span>: לֹא נֶחְלְקוּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Beit Shammai, first and second-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2756\" data-full-name=\"Beit Shammai\" data-name-he=\"בית שמאי\">בֵּית שַׁמַּאי</span> <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Beit Hillel, first and second-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"963\" data-full-name=\"Beit Hillel\" data-name-he=\"בית הלל\">וּבֵית הִלֵּל</span> עַל",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הַמְפוּזָּרִים שֶׁבַּשָּׂדוֹת — שֶׁאֵין מְבִיאִין, וְעַל",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הַמְכוּנָּסִין שֶׁבַּקַּרְפֵּף — שֶׁמְּבִיאִין. עַל מָה נֶחְלְקוּ —",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "עַל הַמְפוּזָּרִים שֶׁבַּקַּרְפֵּף וְעַל הַמְכוּנָּסִין",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שֶׁבַּשָּׂדוֹת, <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Beit Shammai, first and second-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2756\" data-full-name=\"Beit Shammai\" data-name-he=\"בית שמאי\">שֶׁבֵּית שַׁמַּאי</span> אוֹמְרִים: לֹא יָבִיא,",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Beit Hillel, first and second-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"963\" data-full-name=\"Beit Hillel\" data-name-he=\"בית הלל\">וּבֵית הִלֵּל</span> אוֹמְרִים: יָבִיא. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rava, fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2582\" data-full-name=\"Rava\" data-name-he=\"רָבָא\">רָבָא</span>: עֲלֵי",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "קָנִים וַעֲלֵי גְפָנִים, אַף עַל גַּב דִּמְכַנְּפִי לְהוּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וּמוֹתְבִי, כֵּיוָן דְּאִי מִדְּלֵי זִיקָא מְבַדַּר לְהוּ —",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כִּמְפוּזָּרִים דָּמוּ וַאֲסוּרִין. וְאִי אַתְנַח מָנָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מֵאֶתְמוֹל עֲלַיְיהוּ — שַׁפִּיר דָּמֵי<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"165\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"153\" data-sentence-id=\"4\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"ג\"></span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אֵיזֶהוּ קַרְפֵּף",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְכוּ׳<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"166\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> אִבַּעְיָא לְהוּ: הֵיכִי קָאָמַר, כׇּל שֶׁסָּמוּךְ לָעִיר —",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְהוּא דְּאִית לֵיהּ פּוֹתַחַת, וַאֲתָא <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yosei, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1657\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yosei\" data-name-he=\"רבי יוסי בן חלפתא\">רַבִּי יוֹסֵי</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לְמֵימַר: כֵּיוָן דְּאִית לֵיהּ פּוֹתַחַת — אֲפִילּוּ בְּתוֹךְ",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "תְּחוּם שַׁבָּת נָמֵי. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אוֹ דִלְמָא הָכִי קָאָמַר: כׇּל",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שֶׁסָּמוּךְ לָעִיר — בֵּין דְּאִית לֵיהּ פּוֹתַחַת, בֵּין",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְּלֵית לֵיהּ פּוֹתַחַת, וַאֲתָא <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yosei, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1657\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yosei\" data-name-he=\"רבי יוסי בן חלפתא\">רַבִּי יוֹסֵי</span> לְמֵימַר: אֲפִילּוּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּתוֹךְ תְּחוּם שַׁבָּת, וְדַוְקָא דְּאִית לֵיהּ פּוֹתַחַת,",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֲבָל לֵית לֵיהּ פּוֹתַחַת — אֲפִילּוּ סָמוּךְ לָעִיר נָמֵי",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לָא. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"6\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>תָּא שְׁמַע: מִדְּקָתָנֵי, <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yosei, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1657\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yosei\" data-name-he=\"רבי יוסי בן חלפתא\">רַבִּי יוֹסֵי</span> אוֹמֵר: כׇּל שֶׁנִּכְנָסִין",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לוֹ בְּפוֹתַחַת — וַאֲפִילּוּ בְּתוֹךְ תְּחוּם שַׁבָּת, שְׁמַע",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִינַּהּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yosei, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1657\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yosei\" data-name-he=\"רבי יוסי בן חלפתא\">רַבִּי יוֹסֵי</span> תַּרְתֵּי לְקוּלָּא קָאָמַר. שְׁמַע מִינַּהּ.",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Salla, fifth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2378\" data-full-name=\"Rav Salla\" data-name-he=\"רב סלא\">רַב סַלָּא</span> אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Yirmeya bar Taḥlifa II, third and fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1952\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yirmeya bar Taḥlifa II\" data-name-he=\"רבי ירמיה\">רַבִּי יִרְמְיָה</span>: הֲלָכָה",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yosei, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1657\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yosei\" data-name-he=\"רבי יוסי בן חלפתא\">כְּרַבִּי יוֹסֵי</span> לְהָקֵל<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"167\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"154\" data-sentence-id=\"7\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"ד\"></span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"7\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>מַתְנִי׳</strong></big> אֵין מְבַקְּעִין",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "עֵצִים לֹא מִן הַקּוֹרוֹת וְלֹא מִן הַקּוֹרָה",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שֶׁנִּשְׁבְּרָה בְּיוֹם טוֹב. וְאֵין מְבַקְּעִין לֹא בְּקַרְדּוֹם",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְלֹא בִּמְגֵרָה וְלֹא בְּמַגָּל, אֶלָּא בְּקוֹפִיץ<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"168\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>מַתְנִי׳ מְבִיאִין עֵצִים</b> התלושים מן השדה שבתוך התחום ביו\"ט:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>מִן הַמְכוּנָּס</b> אם כנסו מערב י\"ט דגלי דעתיה דעלייהו סמיך ואינו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:1:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מוקצה אבל המפוזרין מוקצין: <b>וּמִן הַקַּרְפֵּף</b> שהוא משתמר ומוקף",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:1:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "סביב אפילו מפוזרים שבו לא הקצה מדעתו: <b>סָמוּךְ לָעִיר</b> ממש:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:1:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>אֲפִילּוּ בְּתוֹךְ תְּחוּם שַׁבָּת</b> בסופו:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:1:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">גמ&#x27;</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">יחידאה</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">היא</span>.</b> רבי שמעון בן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אלעזר קאמר לה דאמר בית הלל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הכי שרו ופליגי רבנן עליה: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">כמפוזרין</span></b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>דָּמוּ.</b> ואפילו לא פזרתן הרוח דמסתמא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לא סמכה דעתיה סבר מבדר להו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "זיקא: <b>וְאִי אַתְנַח מָנָא עֲלַיְיהוּ.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "להכבידן שפיר דמי דסמכה דעתיה:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "רבי יוסי לקולא או לחומרא קאמר לא"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "גרסינן דהא מלתיה דרבי יהודה נמי"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מבעיא לן היכי אתמר וה\"ג אבעיא"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "להו היכי קאמר כל הסמוך לעיר"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "והוא דאית ליה פותחת ואתא ר'"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "יוסי למימר כיון דאית ליה פותחת"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אפי' בתוך תחום שבת נמי או דלמא"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ה\"ק כל שסמוך לעיר בין דאית ליה"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "פותחת בין דלית ליה פותחת ואתא"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "רבי יוסי למימר אפי' בתוך תחום"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שבת ודוקא דאית ליה פותחת אבל"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דלית ליה פותחת אפילו סמוך לעיר"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נמי לא תא שמע מדקתני רבי יוסי"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אומר כל שנכנסין לו בפותחת ואפילו"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בתוך תחום שבת ש\"מ רבי יוסי תרתי"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לקולא קאמר והכי פי' היכי קאמר"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מתני' כל שסמוך לעיר והוא דאית"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ליה פותחת מפתח שמשתמר והאי"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דלא תנא ליה בהדיא משום דקא סבר"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "סתמן יש להן פותחת ואסתם קרפיפות"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אמרה למלתיה ואתא רבי יוסי למימר"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כיון דאית ליה פותחת לא בעינן סמוך"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "וממילא דאי לית ליה פותחת בעינן"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "סמוך ואשתרי בהכי מדתלא שריותא"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בשאין סמוך בפותחת מכלל דסמוך"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בלא פותחת נמי שרי ומיקל בתרתי"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דרבי יהודה בעי. תרוייהו ורבי יוסי"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "סבר בחדא סגי באיזו שתהא שם:"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>אוֹ דִלְמָא.</b> כל שסמוך לעיר דקאמר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ת\"ק בהכי תלא טעמיה כיון דהוי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "סמוך בין דאית ליה פותחת בין דלית",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ליה ואתא רבי יוסי למימר הטעם",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "תלוי בפותחת בין סמוך בין רחוק",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "והכי קאמר כל שנכנסים לו בפותחת הוא דמותר ואפילו הוא בתוך",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "תחום שבת דלא מתלי טעמא בסמיכה כלל: <b>תַּרְתֵּי לְקוּלָּא קָאָמַר.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כלומר מדרבי יוסי נשמע לרבי יהודה דלאו תרוייהו בעי ורבי יוסי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בתרתי אקיל דמכשיר בסמוך בלא פותחת ובפותחת בלא סמוך",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דשמעינן לרבי יהודה דקאמר כל שסמוך לעיר בין דאית ליה פותחת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בין דלית ליה פותחת וא\"ל רבי יוסי כל שיש לו פותחת אפי' הוא בתוך",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "התחום ואי סמוך לא בעי פותחת דאי רבי יוסי בפותחת תלא טעמא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דאפילו הוא סמוך בעי פותחת לא הוה ליה לסיומי ואפילו בתוך",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "תחום שבת אלא הכי הוה ליה למימר רבי יוסי אומר כל שנכנסין לה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בפותחת דכיון דהוה תני כל הוה משמע דצריך פותחת סמוך או",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "רחוק למה לי דסיים ואפילו בתוך תחום שבת אלא לאשמועינן דלא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בעי פותחת אלא למשרי שאין סמוך ורבי יהודה דלא בעי תרתי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נמי מרישא דרבי יוסי שמע מינה מדנקט כל שנכנסין לה בפותחת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כיון דכולהו פותחת אית להו הכי אבעי' ליה למתני רבי יוסי אומר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אפילו בתוך תחום שבת: <b>מַתְנִי׳ אֵין מְבַקְּעִין עֵצִים לֹא מִן הַקּוֹרוֹת</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">כו&amp;#x27</span>.</b> לפי סוגיא של גמרא היא מתפרשת: <b>לא</b> <b>בקרדום.</b> סתם קרדום",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "עשוי כמין כלי אומנות שעושין בו אוכפות וסרגות שקורין איישי\"ש",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ויש שעשוי כעין כלי האומן שקורין בירגוא\"ה שראשו הקצר דומה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לקרדומות שלנו וראשו השני דומה לכלי אומני אוכפות וסרגות",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הסוסים: <b>וְלֹא בִּמְגֵרָה</b> שיג\"ה כעין סכין מלאה פגימות וממהר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:8:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לקוץ בו עצים וכלי אומן הוא: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">מגל</span></b> דולוייר\"א או שרפ\"א וכולן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:8:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כלי אומן הן ונראה כעושה בו מלאכה לפיכך אסור: <b>אֶלָּא בְּקוֹפִיץ.</b> סתם",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:8:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "קופיץ הוא סכין של קצבים דומה לקרדומות שלנו שאינן כלי אומן ויש",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:8:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שעושין בו שני ראשין והשני דומה קצת לקרדום האוכפות כדשמעינן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:8:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מיניה בגמרא ומיהו סתמיה לאו למלאכת אומן הוא: גמ'",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 31a:8:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    }
  ],
